2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with 3D scenes and textures, which are common topics in computer graphics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for solving TILT, which involves optimization and could be considered a machine learning problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image and texture processing, which are common topics in multimedia. 
5. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for optimization, which could be considered a numerical analysis problem.
